pig installation
Download it from here: http://mirrors.aliyun.com/apache/pig/

Sudo vi /etc/profile to add environment variables with below information

PIG_HOME=/[your_path_to_pig]/pig
PIG_CLASSPATH=$HADOOP_HOME/etc/hadoop. — please note it points to Hadoop path
PATH=$PIG_HOME/bin:$PATH
export PIG_HOME
export PIG_CLASSPATH
export PATH


使用， go to command line and type pig:
$PIG_HOME/bin/pig
如果能正常进入grunt > 提示符就表示ok了


See below guide for basic usage:
https://www.cnblogs.com/yjmyzz/p/hadoop-pig-tutorial.html





